  "prompt": "Can somebody tell me a brand of formal shoes that provide same comfort as that of sport shoes?",
  "response": "Certainly! Many brands now focus on combining style with comfort in formal footwear. Here are a few brands you might consider that are known for offering formal shoes with a level of comfort comparable to sports shoes:\n\n1. **Clarks**: Known for their cushioned insoles and supportive designs, Clarks offers a variety of stylish dress shoes that prioritize comfort.\n\n2. **Ecco**: Ecco shoes often feature ergonomic designs and soft materials, providing comfort along with a polished appearance.\n\n3. **Rockport**: This brand incorporates athletic technology into their formal shoes, offering good cushioning and support.\n\n4. **Cole Haan**: Their dress shoes often include cushioning and flexible materials that enhance comfort while maintaining a sophisticated look.\n\n5. **GH Bass**: They offer a range of comfortable loafers and dress shoes that can provide the feel of casual footwear.\n\n6. **Hush Puppies**: Known for their comfort footwear, they also offer a selection of formal styles that use cushioned insoles.\n\n7. **Mephisto**: Though on the higher end of the price spectrum, Mephisto shoes are designed for comfort and feature excellent shock absorption.\n\nWhen shopping, it's a good idea to try on different styles to see which brand and shoe model fit you best in terms of comfort and support.",
